724248f-a.text:
Water Street, south from Beekman to Fulton Streets. At the latter point is the low sloping roofed structure housing the old Brown Pharmacy. To the right appears the easterly side of Beekmah Hiospital (Volunteers of America). Note the 60 Wall Tower and the City Bank Farmers Trust bulldings in the background.
1939
nift of Beecher Ogden
